---
name: Debug Log Session Cleanup
description: Ensures that the vapt-debug.txt file is cleared at the start of a session or task to prevent log bloating.
---

When a new task is initiated or at the start of a session:
- Locate the file `vapt-debug.txt` in the root of the VAPT-Secure plugin directory.
- Clear its contents completely so that debugging starts fresh for the new task.
- Do not delete the file itself, just empty the contents.
